      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>The roiling tumult of the Abyss creates tieflings cursed—or blessed—with the ability to enter frenzies of destructive activity. As a swift action, the tiefling can enter a frenzy, which lasts for 1 minute. During this time, the tiefling takes a –2 penalty to AC and a –1 penalty to all saving throws, but gains a +1 divine bonus to attack rolls and a +2 divine bonus to melee damage rolls. The tiefling can frenzy this way once per day, plus a number of times equal to half their CR or level.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces deceitful and fiendish gloom.</strong></p>\n<p><strong></strong></p><strong></strong><p><strong></strong><em>Update usage in the Details tab as character level allows.</em><strong></strong></p><strong></strong><p><strong></strong></p>"
